Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 稍微有點頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事 從前段時間起就偶爾會出現這種情況的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間就頭痛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這可不像沒事的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 家裏有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不過恕我失陪了 先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
